selector_to_html = {"a[href=\"system.html#lighting-light\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Ilumina\u00e7\u00e3o de Luz<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#lighting-light\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><h3>Habilitado<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#enable\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h3>", "a[href=\"barcode.html#d-symbologies\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Simbologias 1D<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#d-symbologies\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2>", "a[href=\"scanmode.html#key-trigger-mode\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Modo de disparo de chaves<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#key-trigger-mode\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><p>Pressione o bot\u00e3o para acionar a varredura e solte o bot\u00e3o para terminar a verifica\u00e7\u00e3o. A verifica\u00e7\u00e3o termina quando a verifica\u00e7\u00e3o for bem-sucedida ou o tempo de leitura exceder o tempo de leitura \u00fanico.</p>", "a[href=\"character.html\"]": "<h1 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Exterminador<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#terminator\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h1><h2>Finalizar Configura\u00e7\u00f5es do Personagem<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#end-character-settings\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><p>O caractere final \u00e9 adicionado ap\u00f3s os dados decodificados no formato de dados decodificados + caractere final.</p>", "a[href=\"system.html#usb-mode\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Modo USB<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#usb-mode\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><h3>Teclado USB<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#usb-keyboard\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h3>", "a[href=\"scanmode.html#continuous-mode\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Modo cont\u00ednuo<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#continuous-mode\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><p>O scanner funciona continuamente. Se a verifica\u00e7\u00e3o for bem-sucedida ou o tempo de verifica\u00e7\u00e3o exceder o tempo de trabalho \u00fanico, a verifica\u00e7\u00e3o atual termina. Se o tempo exceder o tempo especificado, a pr\u00f3xima verifica\u00e7\u00e3o \u00e9 ativada automaticamente.</p>", "a[href=\"system.html#get-firmware-version\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Obter vers\u00e3o do Firmware<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#get-firmware-version\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2>", "a[href=\"system.html\"]": "<h1 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Configura\u00e7\u00f5es do Sistema<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#system-settings\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h1><h2>Restaurar configura\u00e7\u00f5es padr\u00e3o<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#restore-default-settings\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><p>Quando um erro desconhecido ocorre no scanner, voc\u00ea pode redefinir o scanner restaurando as configura\u00e7\u00f5es padr\u00e3o.</p>", "a[href=\"scanmode.html#auto-sensing-mode\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Modo de Detec\u00e7\u00e3o Autom\u00e1tica<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#auto-sensing-mode\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><p>No modo de detec\u00e7\u00e3o autom\u00e1tica, o scanner detectar\u00e1 o brilho do ambiente ao redor. Quando o brilho muda, a varredura \u00e9 ativada. A verifica\u00e7\u00e3o termina quando a verifica\u00e7\u00e3o for bem-sucedida ou o tempo de verifica\u00e7\u00e3o exceder o tempo de trabalho \u00fanico. Independentemente de a \u00faltima verifica\u00e7\u00e3o ter sido bem-sucedida ou falhada, o brilho do ambiente ao redor ser\u00e1 detectado novamente.</p>", "a[href=\"barcode.html#id1\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Simbologias 2D<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id1\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2>", "a[href=\"keyboard.html\"]": "<h1 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Configura\u00e7\u00f5es de teclado<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#keyboard-settings\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h1><h2>Configura\u00e7\u00f5es de Codifica\u00e7\u00e3o<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#character-encoding-settings\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><h3>GBK(GB2312)<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#gbk-gb2312\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h3>", "a[href=\"barcode.html#block-barcodes-with-urls\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Bloquear c\u00f3digos de barras com URLs<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#block-barcodes-with-urls\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><p>Bloqueie a verifica\u00e7\u00e3o de c\u00f3digos QR de URL come\u00e7ando com <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">http://</span></code>, <code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">https://</span></code></p>", "a[href=\"system.html#volume-settings\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Configura\u00e7\u00f5es de Volume<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#volume-settings\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><h3>Volume baixo<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#low-volume\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h3>", "a[href=\"barcode.html\"]": "<h1 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Simbologias<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#symbologies\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h1><h2>Simbologias 1D<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#d-symbologies\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2>", "a[href=\"system.html#restore-default-settings\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Restaurar configura\u00e7\u00f5es padr\u00e3o<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#restore-default-settings\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><p>Quando um erro desconhecido ocorre no scanner, voc\u00ea pode redefinir o scanner restaurando as configura\u00e7\u00f5es padr\u00e3o.</p>", "a[href=\"keyboard.html#character-encoding-settings\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Configura\u00e7\u00f5es de Codifica\u00e7\u00e3o<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#character-encoding-settings\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><h3>GBK(GB2312)<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#gbk-gb2312\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h3>", "a[href=\"system.html#aiming-light\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Luz Apontada<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#aiming-light\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><h3>Habilitado<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id2\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h3>", "a[href=\"barcode.html#reversal-barcode-settings\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Reverter Configura\u00e7\u00f5es de C\u00f3digo de Barras<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#reversal-barcode-settings\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><h3>Nenhum c\u00f3digo de barras revertido<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#no-support-reversal-barcode\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h3>", "a[href=\"keyboard.html#keyboard-language\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Idioma do teclado<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#keyboard-language\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><h3>chin\u00eas<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#chinese\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h3>", "a[href=\"character.html#end-character-settings\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Finalizar Configura\u00e7\u00f5es do Personagem<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#end-character-settings\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><p>O caractere final \u00e9 adicionado ap\u00f3s os dados decodificados no formato de dados decodificados + caractere final.</p>", "a[href=\"scanmode.html\"]": "<h1 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Modo de Escaneo<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#scan-mode\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h1><h2>Modo de disparo de chaves<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#key-trigger-mode\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><p>Pressione o bot\u00e3o para acionar a varredura e solte o bot\u00e3o para terminar a verifica\u00e7\u00e3o. A verifica\u00e7\u00e3o termina quando a verifica\u00e7\u00e3o for bem-sucedida ou o tempo de leitura exceder o tempo de leitura \u00fanico.</p>", "a[href=\"scanmode.html#scanning-interval\"]": "<h2 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Intervalo de digitaliza\u00e7\u00e3o<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#scanning-interval\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h2><p>Atraso de trabalho ao escanear diferentes c\u00f3digos de barras</p>", "a[href=\"#yx-hs7-wired-scanner-quick-setup-guide\"]": "<h1 class=\"tippy-header\" style=\"margin-top: 0;\">Guia de configura\u00e7\u00e3o r\u00e1pida de escaneamento com fio <strong>YX-HS7</strong><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#yx-hs7-wired-scanner-quick-setup-guide\" title=\"Link to this heading\">#</a></h1>"}
skip_classes = ["headerlink", "sd-stretched-link", "sd-rounded-pill"]

window.onload = function () {
    for (const [select, tip_html] of Object.entries(selector_to_html)) {
        const links = document.querySelectorAll(`article.bd-article ${select}`);
        for (const link of links) {
            if (skip_classes.some(c => link.classList.contains(c))) {
                continue;
            }

            tippy(link, {
                content: tip_html,
                allowHTML: true,
                arrow: true,
                placement: 'auto-start', maxWidth: 500, interactive: false,

            });
        };
    };
    console.log("tippy tips loaded!");
};
